---
title: Not Nonna's Chicken Cacciatore with Cavatappi and Mushrooms
description: Feeding a hungry brood just got easier! Tender chicken gets stewed with Italian-style seasoning, sweet peppers and mushrooms in a savoury tomato sauce, then draped over cavatappi. You won't need to call people to the table; they'll simply follow their noses!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-cacciatore-maison-17eb1430.jpg
